<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <link rel='stylesheet' href='/stylesheets/landing.css' />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Chakra+Petch:ital,wght@1,300&family=Foldit:wght@700&family=Gruppo&family=Libre+Barcode+128+Text&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1><img id='logo-img' src='/images/logo.png'>Chirp</h1>
    <div id='case'>
      <div class='post-preview'>
        <h3>recent chirps</h3>
        <% if (posts.length) { %>
          <% for (let i = 0; i < 3; i++) { %>
            <div class='user-post'>
              <div>
                <img class='user-avatar' src='<%= posts[i].userAvatar %>' alt='avatar'>
              </div>
              <div class='post-content'>
                <p class='user-name'><%= posts[i].userName %></p>
                <p class='post-text'><%= posts[i].content %></p>
              </div>
            </div>
          <% } %>
        <% } %>
      </div>
      <div id='right-case'>
        <div id='intro-text'>
          <p>Chirp is the ultimate platform for letting off steam and getting your frustrations out. 
            Tired of the filtered, picture-perfect world of social media? Look no further, 
            because Chirp is here to provide a safe space for people to vent, complain, 
            and be vulnerable without judgment. Life isn't always rainbows and sunshine, 
            we believe that it's essential to acknowledge and express our frustrations, 
            disappointments, and grievances. This platform is designed exclusively for that purpose - 
            a place where you can let your guard down and be your authentic, unfiltered self.</p>
        </div>
        <a id='login-link' href='/auth/google' class='login'>LOG IN <br> or SIGN UP</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p id='accent-text'>make yourself @ home</p>
  </body>
</html>
